movie_name: Tolkien: Die wahre Geschichte der Ringe
short_description: An early orphan, loving husband and father, J. R. R. Tolkien, who died in 1973, was a novelist, poet, essayist, philologist, professor of Old English and English literature at Oxford University. Underneath his quiet, pipe-smoking ...
